BASE: https://api.b7web.com.br/devsfood/api

GET /api/ping

POST /api/login (email, password)
GET */api/logout

POST /api/user (name, email, password)
GET */api/user
PUT */api/user ([name, email, password, password_confirm, newaddress])

GET /api/categories

GET /api/products ([search, page, category])
GET /api/product/123 

GET /api/deliverycalc ([id_address, street1, zipcode, city, state])
GET /api/cupom (code)

GET */api/user/orders
GET */api/user/order/123
POST */api/user/order (id_address, cupom, products[id, qt], payment_type, delivery_cost, delivery_time)
PUT */api/user/order/123 ([payment_data, payment_status, process_status])

Legenda:
* = endpoint precisa de auth

Formas de envio do AUTH:
- Authorization: Bearer TOKEN
- QueryString token: TOKEN


register -- salvar as informações no localStorage e criar o banco desse usuario no firestore    [✅] criar a estrutura
login -- pegar as informações do usuario e dos pedidos e salvar no localStorage   [✅]
finalizar uma compra -- salvar nova ordem no banco e localstorage   [✅]
limpar historico de ordens -- deletar todas as ordens do banco e localStorage   [✅]
deletar conta -- deletar todos os dados do banco e localStorage   [✅]
logout -- limpar todos os dados do localStorage   [✅]